raw_text = "~ start
## 2pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Jessica: Hey Cub
Jessica: It's your queen
Player: Hi Jessica 👋
Jessica: Well if it isn't the most interesting person on my radar
Jessica: Tell me
Jessica: How do you do it?
Player: Do what? 😅
Jessica: \"Do what\" he says
Jessica: When the queen asks.
Jessica: You answer.
Jessica: You don't play games.
Jessica: I can have you expelled anytime, you know?
Jessica: I could also make sure you never get into another college as well
Jessica: The only job you'd have is sweeping cum off of urinals
Jessica: img: jessica/3
Jessica: You might not believe it now, but do you really wanna test it
Player: Calm down 🙃 I wasn't sure what you were referring to
Jessica: ...
Jessica: You're probably all tensed up right now
Jessica: Relax Cub, I'm only teasing you 😉
Jessica: I'd never do something like that to my loyal little Cub
Jessica: You are my loyal little Cub aren't you?
- Yes
	Player: Yes
- Of course
	Player: Of course
Jessica: Good!
Jessica: What lovely weather we have today, don't you think?
Jessica: img: jessica/4
Player: I guess
Jessica: Anyway
Jessica: About my question
Jessica: I am curious how you were able to bag this girl of yours
Player: Mabel? Why?
Jessica: It's rude to answer a question with another question
Jessica: But you're still new here so I'll let you try again
- She's been my friend for as long as I can remember 😅
	Player: She's been my friend for as long as I can remember 😅
	Jessica: No such thing
	Jessica: We're meant to fuck each other's brains out
	Jessica: Not play friends
- We've been together since the beginning
	Player: We've been together since the beginning
	Jessica: Since the beginning, huh..?
	Jessica: Color me impressed by your adorable little romantic affairs
Jessica: Then if it's truly all that special, why haven't you taken her out on a date?
Player: How did you..?
Jessica: He does it again
Player: I've been busy with work
Jessica: My my, what a cold answer
Jessica: Yet she still follows you around
Jessica: I'm not here to judge you, don't worry
Jessica: You see, I need someone like you
Jessica: There are some girls I'd like to recruit but they're a bit on the stubborn side
Jessica: I need someone who can loosen them up
Player: What do you need me to do exactly?
Jessica: Oh.. nothing you don't want to do
Jessica: Just date and fuck a few girls into submission
Jessica: Then I pull them into the Sorority
Jessica: Doesn't that sound wonderful?
Jessica: Guys dream of this college experience, but you'll get to live it
Jessica: I get what I want, and you'll get what you want
Jessica: And maybe
Jessica: We'll both get a bit more than just that 🫦
Jessica: So, are you in?
- Okay, I'll do it [#purpleheart]
	set Story.flag = \"Jessica1\"
	set Story.purple_heart += 1
	Player: Okay, I'll do it
	Jessica: Just what I like to hear
	Jessica: You'll hear from me again real soon
	Jessica: I've already got someone in mind for you 💜
- I can't do something like that
	Player: I can't do something like that
	Jessica: How disappointing
	Jessica: Maybe Nina was right
	Jessica: Maybe you're just another little Cub who got lucky
	Jessica: We'll see how long that luck holds 😉
=> END
"
